{"tid":778954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河馬牙力驚人可咬穿鱷魚","createTime":"2018-08-14T05:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T06:59:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f06b91ea4006de05022e01eed0204fb124c57ed","tid":778954,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180814/20475894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475894&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=de53e331\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475894&h=48b30907\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180814/20475894</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月14日 <br />\n<br />\n河馬牙力驚人可咬穿鱷魚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180814/large/a1302a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180814%2Flarge%2Fa1302a.gif&h=30cc24a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■發生河馬襲擊遊客的肯雅奈瓦薩湖是著名旅遊景點。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n河馬外表憨厚可愛，其實脾氣暴躁、攻擊性強；河馬有長達50厘米的獠牙，咬合力驚人，連鱷魚都可以咬穿；若河馬認為有人踩場，隨時會發動攻擊，堪稱最凶猛的可愛動物，台北市立動物園非洲動物園區區長高雋表示，河馬微微張開嘴巴其實代表警告。<br />\n<br />\n一位經常帶非洲團的台灣旅遊達人表示，河馬長大後約重2至3公噸，是陸地第3大動物。河馬儘管是草食性動物，但脾氣暴躁，只要認為對方具有威脅，就會發動攻擊，在陸地時速高達45公里，十分危險。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，非洲每年約有200人死於河馬攻擊，單單在肯雅今年有6宗死亡個案。他補充，受全球氣候異常影響，今年肯雅雨多，湖水升高或跟河馬上岸頻率有關，但河馬原則上不會主動攻擊人，提醒有意赴肯雅的遊客不要太靠近野生動物。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n台客遊肯雅遭河馬咬斃　團友回程遇車禍15傷<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n滬黑心疫苗苦主上訪　斥維權難過登天"},{"pid":"7b4de0915c8f8aca3d6496973eb80d5fcbd8c2b5","tid":778954,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"姆明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c2f78df987f14517474b467df3c303b7e4b0fd","tid":778954,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"台灣佬死得好慘 咬心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c858df225f7774b7bbfaf5ba7e48ff9a13d8942","tid":778954,"uid":72328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fqukQRJzS1Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfqukQRJzS1Y&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6b56fa71\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fqukQRJzS1Y</a><br />\n記起呢條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c16bb7329c96c2aed632b10d5190b60a5d1ae40","tid":778954,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"個樣完全係扮豬食老虎"},{"pid":"bbbb667bf5f789e4e3867ae57def0e1a61333013","tid":778954,"uid":177590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"no one fuck with tiny hippo<br />\nAINT NO ONE!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/145804_5c0524e2dc4b91554233d1fd88aec4be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F145804_5c0524e2dc4b91554233d1fd88aec4be.jpg&h=49e8c858&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}